## Uninstallation

To uninstall Device Guardian from the device, remove the Device Guardian client app manually or through an EMM.

### Server Termination

To terminate the Device Guardian cloud server, contact [Zebra services](https://www.zebra.com/us/en/services.html). This removes the cloud server instance and deletes all data stored.

